- `cross-currency-claims-need-an-explicit-transfer-lemma-back-to-the-full-lei-bundle.md`:
  derivative, integrability, surrogate-cancellation, or compactness-side
  gains only count if an explicit transfer lemma brings them back to a
  smaller coefficient on the full LEI bundle.

